# REVORION — Cursor Rules
# Read this before every edit. These rules are non-negotiable.

## Project
Revorion is a B2B enterprise SaaS landing page for revenue leakage detection.
Visual language: cold, precise, institutional. Reference: Palantir investor materials.
Design system tokens are in: styles/revorion-tokens.css — import this first in every CSS file.

---

## Fonts — THREE ONLY

| Role | Font | CSS Variable |
|------|------|-------------|
| Headlines, display | Test Financier Display | var(--font-serif) |
| Body, UI, paragraphs | Test Söhne | var(--font-sans) |
| Buttons, labels, mono UI | Test Söhne Mono | var(--font-mono) |

NEVER use: Inter, Roboto, system-ui, -apple-system, or any other font.

---

## Typography Scale — USE ONLY THESE

```css
/* Headlines — var(--font-serif) */
.type-hero        /* clamp(72px, 12vw, 168px) — hero only, full-bleed */
.type-display     /* clamp(36px, 5vw, 96px) — section openers */
.type-heading     /* 48px fixed */
.type-subheading  /* 32px fixed */
.type-heading-md  /* 24px fixed */

/* Body — var(--font-sans) */
.type-body-lg     /* 18px — intro paragraphs */
.type-body        /* 16px — standard body, NEVER below 16px */
.type-body-sm     /* 14px — secondary descriptions */

/* UI — var(--font-mono) */
.type-micro       /* 12px +5% tracking */
.type-whisper     /* 12px +22% tracking uppercase — section numbers */
.type-button      /* 12.8px +10% tracking uppercase — ALL button labels */
.type-label       /* 11px +8% tracking uppercase */
.type-caption     /* 10px +5% tracking */
```

Rules:
- Body text (type-body, type-body-lg, type-body-sm) NEVER scales — always fixed px
- All mono styles NEVER scale — always fixed px
- Only headline styles use clamp()
- NEVER hardcode font-size values — use the utility classes

