## Responsive Model — HYBRID A+C

Revorion uses a HYBRID approach:
- HeroTitle and Closing CTA: full-bleed, viewport-relative (Obys-style)
- All other content: fluid grid, NO fixed max-width cap, margins switch from px to vw above 1440px

### Breakpoint table

| Breakpoint | Width | Cols | Gutter | Margin | Content | Margin type |
|-----------|-------|------|--------|--------|---------|------------|
| mobile | 375px | 4 | 16px | 20px | 335px | fixed px |
| tablet | 768px | 8 | 24px | 32px | 704px | fixed px |
| laptop | 1024px | 12 | 24px | 48px | 928px | fixed px |
| desktop | 1280px | 12 | 32px | 64px | 1152px | fixed px |
| baseline | 1440px | 12 | 32px | 80px | 1280px | fixed px |
| large | 1920px | 12 | 32px | 5vw | ~1728px | fluid vw |
| QHD | 2560px | 12 | 40px | 8vw | ~2150px | fluid vw |
| 4K | 3840px | 12 | 48px | 12vw | ~2918px | fluid vw |

