## NEVER DO

- border-radius on anything
- hardcode hex colors
- hardcode font-family (use var(--font-*))
- hardcode font-size outside the type scale
- use Inter, Roboto, system-ui
- use gradients
- use blue anywhere
- use box-shadow for decoration
- place two primary buttons in same viewport
- set max-width on .container
- scale body text below 16px
